data.description: This Sunny Taped and Textured 2X6 Construction 2 bedroom 2 bathroom open concept Cavco home is freshly painted and MOVE-in Ready! You will love the Bonus features like Pull out Shelves in many Cabinets, Custom Backsplash in the Island kitchen, Updated Kitchen Flooring, a versatile Murphy Bed in the Guest room. Spacious Primary Suite with a walk-in Closet and more. All on a low maintenance gated and fenced lot. Call today!
